## Configuration

### Environment Variables

**Required for AI features:**
```bash
# ~/.env/gemini.env
GEMINI_API_KEY=AIzaSy...
GEMINI_MODEL=gemini-2.5-flash
```

**Optional:**
```bash
PORT=9123              # API port
HOST=127.0.0.1        # API host
RELAX_STATIC_DIR=...  # Override static dir (dist or public)
```

---

## API Endpoints

### Sessions
- `GET /session?date=YYYY-MM-DD` — Fetch session
- `POST /session` — Save session
- `GET /session/history?limit=10` — Last N sessions
- `GET /session/latest` — Most recent session

### Journal
- `GET /journal?date=YYYY-MM-DD` — Fetch entry
- `POST /journal` — Save entry
- `GET /journal/list` — List entries

### Stats
- `GET /stats/summary?days=14` — Aggregated stats (mood delta, streak, by_technique, per_day)

### Physio
- `POST /api/physio/simulate` — Run simulation

### Knowledge Base
- `GET /api/knowledge/molecule/:id` — Get or AI-generate molecule
- `GET /api/knowledge/search?q=...` — Search molecules
- `GET /api/knowledge/interaction?mol1=X&mol2=Y` — Get interaction
- `GET /api/knowledge/molecules` — List all
- `GET /api/knowledge/reactions` — List all
- `GET /api/knowledge/health` — KB status

### Other
- `GET /techniques` — Available relaxation techniques
- `GET /theme` — Current theme
- `POST /theme` — Set theme
- `GET /health` — Service health

